ried to save the Account object, eitther the Account or ContactDetails object had a reference to a transient object.\r\n\r\nSolution: Save the Account before adding the ContactDetails, so the ContactDetails gets a reference to a persisted Account.','NHibernate Errors','','draft','open','open','','nhibernate-errors','','','2010-06-29 14:27:13','2010-06-29 13:27:13','',0,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/?p=64',0,'post','',0),(65,1,'2010-04-21 11:42:08','2010-04-21 10:42:08','<span> </span>\n<pre>not-null property references a null or transient  valueJiscCollections.Core.Domain.ContactDetails.Account</pre>\nThis happened because of a circular reference. A new (transient) Account object had a new ContactDetails object. When I tried to save the Account object, eitther the Account or ContactDetails object had a reference to a transient object.\n\nSolution: Save the Account before adding the ContactDetails, so the ContactDetails','NHibernate Errors','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision','','','2010-04-21 11:42:08','2010-04-21 10:42:08','',64,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/04/21/64-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(66,1,'2010-04-21 11:43:47','2010-04-21 10:43:47','<span> </span>\r\n<pre>not-null property references a null or transient  valueJiscCollections.Core.Domain.ContactDetails.Account</pre>\r\nThis happened because of a circular reference. A new (transient) Account object had a new ContactDetails object. When I tried to save the Account object, eitther the Account or ContactDetails object had a reference to a transient object.\r\n\r\nSolution: Save the Account before adding the ContactDetails, so the ContactDetails gets a reference to a persisted Account.','NHibernate Errors','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision-2','','','2010-04-21 11:43:47','2010-04-21 10:43:47','',64,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/04/21/64-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(67,1,'2010-04-21 11:47:16','2010-04-21 10:47:16','<span> </span>\n<pre>not-null property references a null or transient value ContactDetails.Account</pre>\nThis happened because of a circular reference. A new (transient) Account object had a new ContactDetails object. When I tried to save the Account object, eitther the Account or ContactDetails object had a reference to a transient object.\n\nSolution: Save the Account before adding the ContactDetails, so the ContactDetails gets a reference to a persisted Account.','NHibernate Errors','','inherit','open','open','','64-autosave','','','2010-04-21 11:47:16','2010-04-21 10:47:16','',64,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/04/21/64-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(68,1,'2010-04-21 11:46:13','2010-04-21 10:46:13','<span> </span>\r\n<pre>not-null property references a null or transient value ContactDetails.Account</pre>\r\nThis happened because of a circular reference. A new (transient) Account object had a new ContactDetails object. When I tried to save the Account object, eitther the Account or ContactDetails object had a reference to a transient object.\r\n\r\nSolution: Save the Account before adding the ContactDetails, so the ContactDetails gets a reference to a persisted Account.','NHibernate Errors','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision-3','','','2010-04-21 11:46:13','2010-04-21 10:46:13','',64,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/04/21/64-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2010-04-29 23:32:20','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Well, I\'m trying to learn Swedish at the moment and have endlessÂ pieces of paper listing SwedishÂ vocabulary, verbÂ conjugations, and phrases. So I\'m planning to create a web app that can hold all these words and allow me to do interesting things with them, which will hopefully help me learn more Swedish.\r\n<h3>NHibernate</h3>\r\nI\'m starting by following the NHibernate guide at http://nhforge.org/wikis/howtonh/your-first-nhibernate-based-application.aspx.\r\n\r\nI\'ve downloaded NHibernate and created a solution with a class library projects for data,